    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "title": "Conclusion: A Call to Action",
      "html": "\n  <section class=\"slide\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 100vh; box-sizing: border-box;\">\n  <style>\n    .slide {\n      background-color: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--text);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      justify-content: center;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 5% 8%;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      position: relative;\n    }\n\n    .content-grid {\n      display: grid;\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n      gap: 3rem;\n      max-width: 1100px;\n      width: 100%;\n    }\n\n    .title {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin-bottom: 2rem;\n      text-align: center;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);\n    }\n\n    .key-takeaways {\n      background: var(--surface);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 1rem;\n      padding: 2.5rem;\n      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n      position: relative;\n    }\n\n    .takeaways-heading {\n      font-family: var(--font-head);\n      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      gap: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .takeaways-heading::before {\n      content: '';\n      width: 4px;\n      height: 1.5rem;\n      background: var(--accent);\n      display: inline-block;\n    }\n\n    .bullet-list {\n      list-style: none;\n      padding: 0;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n\n    .bullet-item {\n      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n      padding-left: 1.5rem;\n      position: relative;\n      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      color: var(--text-muted);\n      transition: color 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .bullet-item:hover {\n      color: var(--text);\n    }\n\n    .bullet-item::before {\n      content: '▹';\n      position: absolute;\n      left: 0;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      font-weight: bold;\n    }\n\n    .bullet-item strong {\n      color: var(--text);\n      display: block;\n      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\n    }\n\n    .cta-box {\n      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--surface), var(--bg));\n      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);\n      padding: 2rem;\n      text-align: center;\n      margin-top: -1rem; /* Moved up as requested */\n      border-radius: 0 1rem 1rem 0;\n      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);\n      font-style: italic;\n      color: var(--text);\n      box-shadow: -10px 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n    }\n\n    .reveal {\n      opacity: 0;\n      transform: translateY(20px);\n      transition: all 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);\n    }\n\n    .reveal.active {\n      opacity: 1;\n      transform: translateY(0);\n    }\n  </style>\n\n  <div class=\"content-grid\">\n    <h1 class=\"title reveal active visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.1s\">Conclusion: A Call to Action</h1>\n    \n    <div class=\"key-takeaways reveal active visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.3s\">\n      <div class=\"takeaways-heading\">Key Takeaways</div>\n      <ul class=\"bullet-list\">\n        <li class=\"bullet-item\">\n          <strong>Scientific Urgency</strong>\n          The window to limit warming to 1.5°C is closing rapidly; systemic transition is no longer optional, but a survival imperative.\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"bullet-item\">\n          <strong>Mitigation Priorities</strong>\n          We must aggressively scale reforestation, deploy industrial-grade carbon capture, and pivot to a circular economy to eliminate waste.\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"bullet-item\">\n          <strong>Policy &amp; Governance</strong>\n          Individual changes are insufficient without binding international treaties that hold corporations and nations accountable.\n        </li>\n        <li class=\"bullet-item\">\n          <strong>Collective Responsibility</strong>\n          The intersection of grassroots activism and high-level policy creates the necessary pressure for structural change.\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cta-box reveal active visible\" style=\"--delay: 0.6s\">\n      \"The future is not something we enter; it is something we create. The tools are ready—the will must now follow.\"\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  \n</section>\n  \n\n\n  ",
